            "size": 267267,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"requests\":[{\"user\":{\"user_id\":\"mYqcsj-MT1atlROpyqC1AQ\",\"photo_url\":\"https:\\/\\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\\/a\\/ACg8ocLATeaBrafQJxYdv8ivS5ufXDxEdJVtn_udvxXDa5E-n66ucsk=s96-c\",\"display_handle\":\"lsom\",\"subscription_plan_id\":null,\"badge\":null},\"user_prompt\":\"A photorealistic close-up photograph of two gloved hands wearing blue disposable nitrile gloves. The hands belong to a researcher, indicated by the white sleeves of a lab coat. The person is holding a smartphone with both hands and is in the act of photographing an object placed on a desk in front of them. The image is taken from a side view, so the phone screen is not visible. The background includes subtle lab details like blurred scientific equipment and a neutral-toned surface. Natural lighting with soft shadows creates a clean, clinical atmosphere. medium close-up, side view, soft lighting, shallow depth of field, photorealism, realistic textures, crisp focus on gloves and phone, subtle background blur\",\"user_negative_prompt\":\"\",\"private\":false,\"request_id\":\"ViMr3bq7SZaHi9QPEkukuA\",\"request_type\":\"TEXT_TO_IMAGE\",\"responses\":[{\"response_id\":\"eIPjz-laRdqQYE7Qd7-kJA\",\"prompt\":\"A photorealistic close-up photograph of two gloved hands wearing blue disposable nitrile gloves. The hands belong to a researcher, indicated by the white sleeves of a lab coat. The person is holding a smartphone with both hands and is in the act of photographing an object placed on a desk in front of them. The image is taken from a side view, so the phone screen is not visible. The background includes subtle lab details like blurred scientific equipment and a neutral-toned surface. Natural lighting with soft shadows creates a clean, clinical atmosphere. medium close-up, side view, soft lighting, shallow depth of field, photorealism, realistic textures, crisp focus on gloves and phone, subtle background blur\",\"self_like\":false,\"num_likes\":0,\"highest_fidelity\":true,\