 steady hands and the clean surgical area. The atmosphere conveys profound isolation and human resilience, with historically accurate 1960s medical equipment and the stark, utilitarian interior design typical of polar research facilities.\",\"self_like\":false,\"num_likes\":0,\"highest_fidelity\":true,\"pin_on_profile\":false,\"cover\":true,\"is_autoprompt\":true,\"private\":false,\"descriptions\":[],\"tags\":[],\"response_index\":2,\"references\":{\"style\":[{\"type\":\"preset_style_type\",\"name\":\"Realistic\",\"deleted\":false,\"style_type\":\"REALISTIC\"}]}}],\"creation_time_float\":1769312471.477522,\"resolution\":1024,\"height\":1024,\"width\":1024,\"user_hparams\":{\"style\":\"AUTO\",\"aspect_ratio\":\"1:1\"},\"seed\":403611438,\"aspect_ratio\":\"1:1\",\"model_version\":\"V_3_1\",\"model_uri\":\"model\\/V_3_1\\/version\\/0\",\"cover_response_id\":\"d6mODdkqRZus1Cqmo9FXew\",\"autoprompt_loading\":false,\"use_autoprompt\":false,\"is_completed\":true,\"is_errored\":false,\"sampling_speed\":0,\"max_upscale_factor\":8,\"can_upscale\":true,\"image_resolution\":\"1K\",\"reference_parents\":[],\"expected_number_of_final_responses\":4,\"character_reference_collection_ids\":[],\"product_reference_collection_ids\":[],\"references\":{\"style\":[{\"type\":\"preset_style_type\",\"name\":\"Auto\",\"deleted\":false,\"style_type\":\"AUTO\"}]},\"style_reference_collection_ids\":[],\"style_expert\":\"AUTO\",\"use_random_style_codes\":false,\"has_started\":true,\"completion_percentage\":100},{\"user\":{\"user_id\":\"8M2cIDx8R6-oscqgpv79vg\",\"photo_url\":\"https:\\/\\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\\/a\\/ACg8ocIqsK13PU4-LGPKSXhFFD3RGI_RpnJL-MaADMtcuzMXqx50oA=s96-c\",\"display_handle\":\"rajkaushal73100\",\"subscription_plan_id\":null,\"badge\":null},\"user_prompt\":\"A professional electrician wearing a safety uniform and gloves, standing on a ladder, inspecting or installing a ceiling-mounted smoke alarm in a modern home. The electrician is focused, holding tools, and examining the